text: KNNU (92.3 FM) is a radio station licensed to Antlers, Oklahoma, United States. The station is currently owned by Payne 1 Communications LLC ==History== This station was assigned call sign KNNU on December 17, 2009. ==References== ==External links== *http://k955.com/payneradiogroup/images/kqik/KQIK-KNNU%20coverage%20map.jpg NNU Category:Country radio stations in the United States Category:Radio stations established in 2015
